question: What are the brick points in this graph?
Can you find nodes that has information about an external reference?
generated_sparql:
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
PREFIX dcterms: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/>
PREFIX schema: <http://schema.org/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?node ?externalReference WHERE {
  ?node ?p ?externalReference .
  FILTER(?p IN (rdfs:seeAlso, owl:sameAs, schema:sameAs, dcterms:references))
}
